				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Dialogue with the ghost of Amelyssan, bound to eternal service to Bhaal in her afterlife. In \"Baldur's Gate 2: Throne of Bhaal\", she attempted to usurp Bhaal's portfolio of murder and absorb Bhaal's essence. Now she is no more than a spectral slave."
